00:04:33.640 --> 00:04:37.000
Rarely is the trial ever come the same way,

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:41.320
and they come in variety of ways and a variety of times.

00:04:41.320 --> 00:04:44.220
And you might find that at times a trial will come

00:04:44.220 --> 00:04:45.839
