and you understand the context,

00:06:43.920 --> 00:06:46.559
a different type of temptation

00:06:46.559 --> 00:06:49.839
than the temptation that we read of in verses two through 12

00:06:49.839 --> 00:06:52.279
the temptation that we deal with in verses two through 12

